g.title: Sheet.1147
g.desc: *1 hour per 1 transfer If DTD both in A and B destination -> ...
g.text: *1 hour per 1 transferIf DTD both in A and B destination -> 2 transfers to Truck -> 2 x 1 hour -> 2 hours** If DTD when Truck as main transport ( for A –> B), there is just the extra time for the additional DTD destination(s) to drive. No change of Truck.
